{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"SVG image element","mdn_url":"/ru/docs/Web/SVG/Tutorial/SVG_Image_Tag","locale":"ru","native":"Русский","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><ul class=\"prev-next\">\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/ru/docs/Web/SVG/Tutorial/SVG_fonts\">« Предыдущая статья</a></li>\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/ru/docs/Web/SVG/Tutorial/Tools_for_SVG\">Следующая статья  »</a></li>\n</ul><p></p>\n\n<p>SVG тег <a href=\"/ru/docs/Web/SVG/Element/image\"><code>&lt;image&gt;</code></a> позволяет выводить растровые изображения внутри SVG-объектов.</p>\n\n<p>В примере ниже растровое изображение <strong>a.jpg</strong>, заданное при помощи атрибута <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/href\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">href (en-US)</a></code>, отображено внутри SVG-объекта:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: xml notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token prolog\">&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\" standalone=\"no\"?&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">DOCTYPE</span> <span class=\"token name\">svg</span> <span class=\"token name\">PUBLIC</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"-//W3C//DTD SVG 1.1//EN\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"http://www.w3.org/Graphics/SVG/1.1/DTD/svg11.dtd\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>svg</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>5cm<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>4cm<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">version</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>1.1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n     <span class=\"token attr-name\">xmlns</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.w3.org/2000/svg<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">xmlns:</span>xlink</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>image</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">xlink:</span>href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>firefox.jpg<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">x</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>0<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">y</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>0<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>50px<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>50px<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>svg</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n\n<div class=\"warning notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p>Важные замечания (подробнее <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/struct.html#ImageElement\" rel=\" noopener\">W3 specs</a>):</p>\n</div>\n\n<ul>\n <li>\n  <p>Если параметры <strong>x</strong> или <strong>y</strong> не заданы, то им будут присвоены значения равные <strong>0</strong>.</p>\n </li>\n <li>\n  <p>Если параметры <strong>height</strong> или <strong>width</strong> не заданы, то им будут присвоены значения равные <strong>0</strong>.</p>\n </li>\n <li>Если значение любого из параметров изображения <strong>height</strong> или <strong>width</strong> равны <strong>0</strong>, то отображение отключено.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></p><ul class=\"prev-next\">\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/ru/docs/Web/SVG/Tutorial/SVG_fonts\">« Предыдущая статья</a></li>\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/ru/docs/Web/SVG/Tutorial/Tools_for_SVG\">Следующая статья  »</a></li>\n</ul><p></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"SVG тег <image> позволяет выводить растровые изображения внутри SVG-объектов.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"SVG image element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"SVG: Elément image","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"SVG の image 要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"SVG 이미지 요소","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"SVG image element","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ru/web/svg/tutorial/svg_image_tag","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ru/web/svg/tutorial/svg_image_tag/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ru/docs/Web","title":"Веб-технологии для разработчиков"},{"uri":"/ru/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG"},{"uri":"/ru/docs/Web/SVG/Tutorial","title":"SVG — учебное руководство"},{"uri":"/ru/docs/Web/SVG/Tutorial/SVG_Image_Tag","title":"SVG image element"}],"pageTitle":"SVG image element - SVG | MDN","noIndexing":false}}